-- UBS Recruits Rothschild’s Grafstein as Co-Head of Americas M&A
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   R .   M i d e r
-- 2012-08-21T19:41:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/ubs-recruits-rothschild-s-grafstein-as-co-head-of-americas-m-a.html
UBS AG (UBSN) , Switzerland’s biggest bank,
hired Laurence Grafstein from Rothschild to be co-head of
mergers and acquisitions for the Americas.  Grafstein will work alongside the other co-head, Marc-
Anthony Hourihan, Zurich-based UBS said today in an internal
memorandum obtained by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zachary R. Mider in New York at 
 zmider1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeffrey McCracken at 
 jmccracken3@bloomberg.net  